Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm of the wind clears reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the black conspiracies and the alibis are revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A case that has not been resolved in this immense house,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A spicy deduction does the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To recognize only one truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intelligence of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko had invited Ran, Kogoro, and myself to Kariorizawa for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were on our way to her summer house...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the trip the flooded river, due to the rain, took the car away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is how we ended up in a remote house in the middle of the forest and spent the night there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that night, Iwao Akashi, the owner of the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was found dead in his bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm Yamamura, from Gunma's police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask you a few questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course. How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is evidence around your father's wrist showing that his hands were tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you thought why that could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like someone tided him up real good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surely they must have been rubber bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father had the bad habit of putting together all types of rubber bands...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and he always wore them around his wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was already starting to think it was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you were starting to think something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, we found a bunch of rubber bands under his pillow, so we thought it could be something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that is all you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps you remember seeing someone suspicious around the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe, you might have heard a weird sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, now that you mentioned it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mentioned it, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no it's nothing, but when I went upstairs for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that the old man was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard him crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surely he was crying after deciding to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see anything else in the bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be talking, calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was a napkin on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he must have used it to wipe his mouth while he was eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because we found curry stains on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my deduction is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iwao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't go to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why he was bleeding from the mouth was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...surely it's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! don't touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, it's just like I thought it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they did the extraction three days ago, his gums shouldn't have healed yet and still be a little open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his gums are still open and there's no sign that they've healed too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neither is there evidence to show that the gums had stopped bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thinking differently, this is evidence that someone pulled out his tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also, the surrounding teeth were affected as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this means that his tooth was pulled out violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already discovered where this trick is going,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this happened how I think it should have happened, then it has to be somewhere in the edges of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it not in sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, and now what do we do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about this curry and rice that's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's not poisoned; do you want it taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Mr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want kid? Don't tell me what you want is to eat it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Enough, is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! I found it, it's this, and I have no doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey kid, Is that a tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what are you saying? A human tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:06:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt, the person who killed Iwao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} set up a plan so that he had an excuse, and that person is Akashi Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, and now, to get everyone together at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And start the spectacle of deductions of sleeping Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do with the tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to tell Inspector Yamamura what we found...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... excuse me... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My... My voice is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just when I figured out the case, I can't use the voice transformer to reveal the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could write it, but I can't with my broken wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to make them find out... the truth themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The investigator and officers have to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... can't... talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, that now you lost your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, we told you not to talk because you would lose your voice, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think this case is pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 7:30 Iwao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died in his room on the second floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people that were in the house at the time include... Ran, Sonoko, Conan, and Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. They were in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they have an excuse. And I was taking a shower, but I didn't have a motive, neither did I have the time to prepare anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And plus, an hour before we found the body a light in the bedroom was on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we found the body the light was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has all the signs of a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing we can think happened is that Iwao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} turned of the light and committed suicide, so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recommend you to stop investigating and return to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, your wrong, this is a homicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has prepared a trick so it looks like the victim would have committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The assassin is the son of Iwao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how can do this, I can't blame him for the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I can't talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, this is going to be a bit difficult but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's communicating with signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what? You want to eat 14 rice balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A different ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, it should be... an oatmeal cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! I know, a different... a weird thing, It could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what's so weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curry, did something happen to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was spicy, but good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's not that, then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, Sonoko, Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man on the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, Thirty... You referring to my age? I'm 33 years old, yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your referring to the amount of curry that we ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and me ate one plate, but Hirota's father ate three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's so strange about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is weird, It's a coincidence that you and your group are here, and that Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lives alone with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because your the only two that live here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's weird to make curry for 7 people, when in reality only two people live here, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, now that you say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...like curry a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also like a lot of curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:11:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I made extra because I sometimes invite my students that are friends of mine, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like they really like the curry with rice that I make.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'m not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, too bad that it rained today and there was no one at the tennis courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teeth... curry... bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Curry is bad... for your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's saying that when you have a tooth extraction you shouldn't eat spicy foods, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, didn't the dentist tell you that you shouldn't eat spicy foods when he fixed your cavities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah your right. But then, this is really weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew that your father had a tooth extracted two or three days ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew he went to the dentist but I didn't know he had a tooth extraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura, can you come with me for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is... Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The forensic came and examined the body, he said that Iwao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s tooth wasn't extracted three days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and that the extracted tooth was found in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason... it was found in the plate of rice and curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there some tough meat in the curry, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think the meat was too tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He? He... has... chewed... one... thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean gums?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he was chewing, he was eating rice with curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You grab the tie from the back, and then you get to the end of the tie and... you bite it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hung from the rope biting with his gums, Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way, he would get tired of biting the rope and it would be inevitable that he would be hanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His tooth fell in the plate of curry the moment the rope pulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he was using his mouth he couldn't cry or do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean what I heard wasn't him crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could swear I heard someone moaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was no trace of the rope being in the mouth of Iwao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But surely... the napkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found a napkin with a stain of curry close to the body, he put the napkin around the rope and made him bite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:14:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An effect, that way there wouldn't be traces of the rope in his mouth, but when we found him, his hands were not tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he grabbed the rope with his hands he would have released his mouth and screamed "Somebody help me!", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the light that was on for an hour and half, was off when we found the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All this time, no one had entered the room, so no one could have turned off the light... kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan enough, don't play with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His hands were tied with the lights cord in a special knot, so when he got tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the rope would leave his mouth and the body would fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would break his neck and at the same time the lights cord would stretch and turn off the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cord that tied his hands would be released and the body would fall into the same position as we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iwao Akashi's wrists demonstrate that he was tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this type of light has three types of brightness, if the cord is not pulled three times, it won't turn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pulling it once turns off the exterior light, pulling twice leaves the small orange light on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you adjust the brightness to the second type and the orange light is off, the light would turn off with one pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, can it be untied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean this cord is tied to make it longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forcefully tying someone with this type of string, it's impossible while the cord is still connected to the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...furthermore, a complicated knot cannot be undone just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th... This is a fishing knot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how you tie a fishing string...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This type of string needs to be tied that way so it doesn't come undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember that Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wife bought a fishing book?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to tie the cord so that it wouldn't become undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how is it that the one in the bedroom is different?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've noticed that the string in the bedroom is tied with a normal knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I understand, that explains why the cord is shorter in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't undo the knot so he must have cut it with scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was a normal knot because the assassin didn't know how to do a fishing knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:17:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or am I wrong, Akashi's Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've done it the following way, you delivered Iwao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s curry to his bedroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was eating, you covered his mouth with the napkin from behind, and tied him with the light cord you had cut with some scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then after putting the rope around his neck, you made him bite the rope together with the napkin and left him suspended in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And naturally, you threatened him that if he let go of the rope, he would die hanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, the only thing you had to do was tie the cord that you tied his hands with, to the light cord on the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you made someone go to the bedroom to look for the plate of curry and rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You warned the person that was supposed to pick up the plate not to enter if the light was on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:18:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First you said to go 10 min after you came back from the second floor because you supposed he was still holding the rope with his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you returned to ask her to go again in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one that sees that the light is off, enters and finds the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...since you were with us in the living room you had an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So your saying that Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was at the tennis courts to invite someone, so that he could give evidence of his excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, He prepared a large amount of curry on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if... if we hadn't come, all this wouldn't have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well no, even if you guys hadn't come, I would have killed him by nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that today is my wife's death anniversary...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, they found my wife in the woods completely decomposed because of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? She was in the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it happened a day I went to work at a tennis court in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dad woke up my wife that was sleeping to recuperate of a cold that she had and he made her go buy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to eat rice with mushrooms, she could have declined, but she didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She did everything she could to go the supermarket that was miles away from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And like predicted, she fainted and there she stayed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that is not enough reason to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I decided to kill him a day after my wife's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moment the he thought that I wasn't there, my father let out a few words in front of my mothers grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistress, It has finally been broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope next time Hirota has a healthier woman, a toy that will last as long as Hirota.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You commented before that you were adopted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:20:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understood his egotistic attitude was because he already considered me his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he built a house in the woods and we started living here, my father, my wife and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because my father wanted to live apart from the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also what happened with the light cord was, he ordered that they be made longer not only the ones in his room but all the ones in the house in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the cord from the ceiling in that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was the only cord my father tied, a normal knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was a knot made by my wife... I wouldn't be able to cut it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...surely I would have had remorse when I committed this crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.38,0:22:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lets see! What an uncomfortable case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's natural since a person died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro and I,Sonoko, the queen of deductions, we resolved the case in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I forgot to film the spectacle of the deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you started without sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha, This time I'm twice as tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:23:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... It looks like I received a call last night, but the number is blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, If you mean the one when you were in the bathroom, he answered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it a call from Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From your face It must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what did he say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.64,0:23:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... sorry, if I've made you worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't a bra size X?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.81,0:23:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you use a bra size X, then it's like saying your breast are 70 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, are your breasts that big?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not! I'm not a cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have to send her a message later...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10 Million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've told me that a person of their house has a purpose to kill her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll pay me 10 million yen if I discover who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I think really hard and have a little luck I'll have it resolved in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.81,0:24:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One moment, don't fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Similar Princess (Part 1)!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.79,0:24:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
